# Test Workflow

*Last validated: 2026-05-10*

- Keep tests next to the production module they exercise.
- Name the observable behavior in the `describe` block.
- Add or update one focused assertion per behavior change.
- Prefer tiny fixtures over broad integration setup in this sample repo.
